    display: block;
  }

  .menu-toggle-checkbox:checked + .menu-toggle-label + .menu {
    display: flex;
  }
}
```

### Explanation

- **Dropdown Menu**: Each menu item with sub-options (`.has-submenu`) contains a nested `ul` for the dropdown. The dropdown menu appears when the user hovers over the parent item (`.has-submenu:hover .submenu`).
- **Hover Effects**: The hover effect changes the text color when the user's cursor passes over a menu item (`a:hover`).
